query:
SELECT p.id, p.assessmentId, p.url, p.caption, a.componentCode, a.componentName 
FROM photos p 
LEFT JOIN assessments a ON p.assessmentId = a.id 
WHERE p.assessmentId IS NOT NULL AND p.deletedAt IS NULL
LIMIT 10;
